<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-STARWARS-MADNESS01-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    `The Force' is looming and stronger than ever
 &HT;    By Michael Browning
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ There is a great disturbance in the
Force.
</P>
<P>
   ``Star Wars: Episode 1 _ The Phantom Menace,'' George Lucas'
$115 million prequel to the phenomenally successful ``Star Wars''
trilogy launched 22 years ago, hangs over an awestruck America this
May the way the Death Star once loomed above the peaceful planet of
Alderaan. It opens May 19 in 3,600 theaters across the country.
</P>
