   POLITICS
</P>
<P>
   BUSH _ AUSTIN, Texas _ The primary is about 10 months away, but
there is no shortage of presidential candidates wandering the towns
of New Hampshire. Missing in action is George W. Bush, the
frontrunner who says he is too busy being governor to campaign for
president. But Bush, in absentia, is putting together a full-time
campaign in this crucial state. A look at the candidateless
campaign. (Herman, Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
<P>
   LAURABUSH _ AUSTIN, Texas _ A profile of Laura Bush, including
why Texas' First Lady has thought twice about the chance to become
the nation's First Lady. (Bonnin, Austin American-Statesman). 96.
WITH PHOTOS. MOVED
</P>
<P>
   GORE _ CARTHAGE, Tenn. _ Behind Vice President Al Gore the
stiff, cerebral politician is Al Gore the warm, relaxed, funny
family man. A personality profile of Gore as seen by his family and
friends, and in the context of his upbringing and early career.
150. (Reid, Palm Beach Post). WITH PHOTOS.
