   LAWYER _ WASHINGTON _ Cyrus Mehri is a first generation
Iranian-American, a New Yorker with a touch of the South through
his South Carolina-born wife. He's going to get even closer to the
South in what could be a three-four year odyssey of trying a
discrimination suit against Coca-Cola. (McNaughton, Cox News
Service). 30. WITH PHOTO. MOVED Thursday.
</P>
