   DOLLHOUSES _ WASHINGTON _ A Palm Beach, Fla., woman has donated
four intricately decorated dollhouses to the National Society
Daughters of the American Revolution. (Palm Beach Post)
</P>
<P>
   With photos. MOVED Tuesday.
