<P>
   NBA
</P>
<P>
   BKN-JORDAN-HORNETS _ Michael Jordan's pending part-ownership of
the Charlotte Hornets is partly resulting from an effort by
commissioner David Stern to interrupt the all-white ownership of
NBA teams. Black men have been involved in ownership before but
didn't last long, partly because of not-deep-enough pockets. That's
no problem for Jordan _ and others from the entertainment world,
ranging from Bill Cosby to Master P, are interested, too. (Bunn,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 60. MOVED
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-FEATURE _ NBA feature on Boston, New Jersey and other
teams whose disappointing seasons end this week before the
playoffs. (Denberg/Bunn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-NOTES _ Our beat writers hand out awards for the season.
(Denberg/Bunn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBA-WESTNOTES _ Western Conference notes. (Denberg, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). MOVED
</P>
