<HEADLINE>
CAROLINA BANK ROBBERIES SHOW   THAT FRIENDLINESS CARRIES A PRICE 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (REPEATING for all needing.)  
 (ATTN: Calif., Wash., N.J.)   (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also filed in category code ``a.'')  
