SEX-OFFENDER _ If Brad Farabough sends a birthday card to a niece
or nephew, he's a step closer to going back to jail. If he opens
the door to neighborhood kids, he could be back behind bars. As a
registered sex offender, Farabough is feeling the full weight of a
national push to keep closer tabs on an estimated 200,000
registered sex offenders who are out in the community. By KATHLEEN
INGLEY. Story will move in the ``a'' category. &QL; 
