mountaintops Saturday to a gathering of the National Rifle
Association faithful. He stood in a fancy hotel ballroom only a few
miles from the worse high school shooting spree in U.S. history,
and by his presence alone implied the original stone tablets
contained a typographal error in line six. As if it should have
read, `Thou SHALT kill.' By E.J. MONTINI. Story will move in the
